HOUSE BILL 1181
By Hicks T
SENATE BILL 925
By Jackson
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 67,
Chapter 6, Part 3, relative to taxation of broadband
equipment and services.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 67-6-391(a), is amended by deleting
the language "through June 30, 2025,".
SECTION 2. The Tennessee Code Commission is requested to amend the heading to
Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 67-6-391, to read "Tennessee broadband equipment and
services exemption.".
SECTION 3. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
